            td string
            td 
            td Actions label color. One of <a href="../docs/color-themes.html">default colors</a>
          tr
            td bold
            td boolean
            td 
            td Defines whether the label text is bold or not
          tr
            th(colspan="4") &lt;ActionsButton&gt; properties
          tr
            td color
            td string
            td 
            td Actions button color. One of <a href="../docs/color-themes.html">default colors</a>
          tr
            td bold
            td boolean
            td 
            td Defines whether the button text is bold or not
          tr
            td close
            td boolean
            td true
            td Should Action Sheet be closed on button click or not
      h2 Event Properties
      table.events-table
        thead
          tr
            th Event
            th Description
        tbody
          tr
            td actions:open
            td Event will be triggered when Action Sheet starts its opening animation
          tr
            td actions:opened
            td Event will be triggered after Action Sheet completes its opening animation
          tr
            td actions:close
            td Event will be triggered when Action Sheet starts its closing animation
          tr
            td actions:closed
            td Event will be triggered after Action Sheet completes its closing animation
      h2 Methods
      table.methods-table
        tr
          td .open(<span>animated</span>)
          td Open Action Sheet
        tr
          td .close(<span>animated</span>)
          td Close Action Sheet
      h2 Open and close Action Sheet
      p You can control Action Sheet state, open and closing it:
      ul
        li using its <a href="../docs/action-sheet.html#create-and-open-action-sheet">JavaScript API</a>
        li by passing <b>true</b> or <b>false</b> to its <code>opened</code> prop
